This paper is about natural language representations and their pre-training, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses model compression techniques and knowledge distillation, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL, followed by the four machine learning sub-categories in descending order of likelihood.
